milestones.description: Paras Khadka and Khakurel's 29-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between Paras Khadka and Malla
Khakurel and Airee's 58-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 25 between Paras Khadka and Airee
